column5: HI there, You've heard about the fishing in the Bay of Quinte and the size of the of the fish. Well, here's a tv show that shows them. You can watch it with media player.www.gettinghooked.net/Episodes.htm David Delcloo aka Superdad
wow, took about ten minutes to down load but what an awsome 1/2 hour television show. really enjoyed it. big walleyes! scar
It helps to have HIGH speed connectivity. David Delcloo aka Superdad
David That was quite representative of the fishing that can be had on the bay of quinte...Larry
